cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with video-based human activity recognition using deep convolutional neural networks. 
2. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is also likely as the paper uses large text corpora to relate objects and activities for learning a unified CNN. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses multitask learning to improve activity recognition performance. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with developing a novel approach for activity recognition using object and text-guided semantics. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with video-based activity recognition.
